content: BY THEIR DEEDS, (YOU) WILL, KNOW THEM !! ETERNITY, IN HELL AWAITS (ALL) THOSE, THAT WORSHIP SATAN ! THEIR WEALTH, WILL BE AS MILLSTONES, AROUND THEIR NECKS, AND GOD'S CURSE, WILL BE UPON THEM, AND ON THEIR DAY OF JUDGEMENT, THEY, WILL HEAR THOSE FATEFULL WORDS, " DEPART FROM ME THOU CURSED, I KNOW YE NOT" !! 🥺😖😫😱☠☝🤲🙏👏👏
